kdna-remote-server
Copyright 2026 KDNA Authors

This product includes software developed at
https://github.com/aikdna/kdna-remote-server

This server is a structural selection layer for KDNA `.kdna`
assets in `remote` access mode. It does not transmit, store, or
certify judgment content. See LICENSE for the full Apache 2.0
license text. See README.md for the self-hosting invariant and
layer-isolation guarantees.

The forbidden content-trust vocabulary (`official`, `trusted`,
`recommended`, `high_quality`, `quality_badge`,
`officially_approved`) is structurally excluded from server
responses per SPEC §13.1 and the layer isolation rules in
`docs/REMOTE_MODE.md`.
